cci (1, 2, 3, 5, 8, 13...).\")]),e(\"li\",{staticClass:\"mb-0\"},[e(\"i\",{staticClass:\"fas fa-arrow-circle-right\"}),a._v(\"Cada miembro estima en secreto el esfuerzo y se comparan las respuestas para discutir discrepancias.\")])])])]),e(\"div\",{staticClass:\"col-lg-4 mb-4\",attrs:{\"data-aos\":\"zoom-in-up\"}},[e(\"div\",{staticClass:\"bg-color-white box-shadow px-4 py-5 h-100\"},[e(\"img\",{staticClass:\"mx-auto d-block mb-4\",staticStyle:{width:\"90px\"},attrs:{src:s(\"7500\"),alt:\"\"}}),e(\"h4\",{staticClass:\"mb-2 text-center\"},[a._v(\"T-Shirt Sizing\")]),e(\"ul\",{staticClass:\"lista-ul--color color-dark\"},[e(\"li\",{staticClass:\"mb-0\"},[e(\"i\",{staticClass:\"fas fa-arrow-circle-right\"}),a._v(\"Se utiliza cuando los requerimientos aún son vagos. Se asignan tamaños tipo S, M, L, XL a las tareas.\")]),e(\"li\",{staticClass:\"mb-4\"},[e(\"i\",{staticClass:\"fas fa-arrow-circle-right\"}),a._v(\"Útil en etapas iniciales de proyectos grandes.\")])])])]),e(\"div\",{staticClass:\"col-lg-4 mb-4\",attrs:{\"data-aos\":\"zoom-in-up\"}},[e(\"div\",{staticClass:\"bg-color-white box-shadow px-4 py-5 h-100\"},[e(\"img\",{staticClass:\"mx-auto d-block mb-4\",staticStyle:{width:\"90px\"},attrs:{src:s(\"b915\"),alt:\"\"}}),e(\"h4\",{staticClass:\"mb-4 text-center\"},[a._v(\"Three-Point Estimation\")]),e(\"ul\",{staticClass:\"lista-ul--color color-dark\"},[e(\"li\",{staticClass:\"mb-0\"},[e(\"i\",{staticClass:\"fas fa-arrow-circle-right\"}),a._v(\"Se calcula el promedio ponderado de tres escenarios: optimista, más probable y pesimista.\")]),e(\"li\",{staticClass:\"mb-0\"},[e(\"i\",{staticClass:\"fas fa-arrow-circle-right\"}),a._v(\"Permite calcular el riesgo asociado a tareas inciertas.\")])])])])])},function(){var a=this,t=a.$createElement,e=a._self._c||t;return e(\"div\",{staticClass:\"bg-full-width bg-color-3 mb-5\"},[e(\"div\",{staticClass:\"px-4 px-md-5 py-4 text-white\"},[e(\"div\",{staticClass:\"row align-items-center\"},[e(\"div\",{staticClass:\"col-lg-auto\"},[